Microcontroller: Atmel AtMega328: http://www.digikey.com/product-detail/en/ATMEGA328-AUR/ATMEGA328-AURCT-ND/3440951

RGB LEDs: Adafruit white LEDs with integrated drivers: http://www.adafruit.com/products/1655

Power Supply: 18650 Li-Ion cells (around 3300mAh each, 4.7V output) - From a guy on laserpointerforums.com

